      <p>Life can be so many things at once - busy, exciting, stressful, joy filled, sad, and even shocking - but through it all God’s grace is always present. <em>Everything is Grace</em> is a podcast dedicated to helping you see God’s hand in your everyday moments and encounters —whether in the joys, the struggles, or the quiet in-between. </p>
      
