      <span>MEET YOUR HOST</span>
      <h2>Kara Loryn Lilly</h2>
      <p>You may know me as a Christian wedding photographer, a former health coach, a youth minister, a speaker, or maybe a worship leader. No matter how our paths have crossed, at the heart of it all, I’m a storyteller and disciple, passionate about helping others discover the meaning of the Gospel in their everyday lives.</p>
      <p>I believe discipleship isn’t a set of rules; it’s a daily invitation to follow Christ in every season, every calling, and in the culture and environment around us. <em>Everything is Grace</em> is where all of our passions meet—a space to explore faith, purpose, relationships, and the ways God speaks through our stories and the world around us.
      </p>
